; FILED: the VM exits 0 even after a fatal runtime error.
; native -r : nonzero exit
; vm        : prints "ERROR: calling non-function" on stderr, exit code 0.
; Consequence: exit codes cannot distinguish VM success from failure;
; run_vm_parity.sh greps stderr for ERROR/WARNING markers instead.
(display (this-function-does-not-exist 1))
